netflix and chill.author: Andrew W.
netflix and chill.review: Soooo i ordered from here on caviar delivery when my girlfriend and I were too lazy to go out and get ice cream. We thought their package names like "Netflix and chill" and "get lucky" we're hilarious but overpriced. We got the "get lucky" which was two pints and a small container of bourbon caramel. When the order arrived we laughed really hard when we opened the package as we finally found out why it costs so much; they delivered two condoms along with our ice cream lol. This is probably the next best thing for my single friends since tinder lol
